      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p138_s0028",
      "text": "The FFI_RTM ELS Request shall request the Domain Controller of the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        635.02,
        409.39,
        646.14
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p138_s0029",
      "text": "AE Principal Switch to return",
      "bbox": [
        412.44,
        635.02,
        539.93,
        646.14
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p138_s0030",
      "text": "the current Domain Topology Map in the LS_ACC Reply Sequence.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        394.85,
        658.14
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p138_s0031",
      "text": "Support for this ELS is mandatory for a Domain Controller in an AE Principal Switch or an AE Switch",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        671.02,
        540.08,
        682.14
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p138_s0032",
      "text": "that is capable of becoming an AE Principal Switch. Support for this ELS is optional for Nx_Ports.  ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        683.02,
        530.32,
        694.14
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
